title: Degenerates
description: Reckless. Wild. Legends.   Adelaide. Reckless. Debauched. Savage princess.  Zane. Wild. Depraved. Venomous prince.  One midsummer night that cruel bitch called, fate, decided we needed to meet, setting off a chain of events that would change both of our lives forever.  Hating him was innate. Loving him was unexpected.  I was the nitro. He was the dynamite.  Together we were catastrophic.
author: Natalie Bennett
